translation:
Principal Biscotti$n$
@I don't want them to know about our plans. I won't ask for all the children.$n$
Half is enough. I want them to return, trained as wizards who can fight on the front line.

Pizza$n$
@Let's...$pause$ teleport!$n$
No matter where you are, I can pull you out of my silk hat like a rabbit!

Pizza$n$
@If you pay me $red$5 |\00\0ePine Cones$black$, I'll register this as a warp spot. Once this is registered as a warp spot, you can warp here no matter where you are. To warp, first select $red$All Files$black$ in your $red$menu$black$ and then select the $red$World Map$black$. Align the quill with the place you want to go, press the $red$A button$black$, and you'll warp there!$n$
Do you want to register this warp spot?

Pizza$n$
@If you pay me $red$5 |\00\0ePine Cones$black$, I'll register this as a warp spot. Once this is registered as a warp spot, you can warp here no matter where you are.$n$
Do you want to register this warp spot?

Pizza$n$
@This is already registered as a warp spot!$n$
See you!

$Miss Madeleine$$n$
@You two are late!$n$
Hurry up!

Balsamico$n$
@Ready...$pause$ set...$pause$$n$
GOOOOOOO!

Brownie$n$
@Feel free to kick the peculiar thing.$n$
Uh huh.

\86\0c$n$
@Hey everyone! It isn't free time yet!$n$
$Miss Madeleine$'s going to get mad at us!

\86\0c$n$
@Sheesh!$n$
You guys!

\86\0c$n$
@There were a lot of gummy frogs over there in the forest! If you eat a gummy frog, you'll recover HP.$n$
I want to catch some too!

\86\02$n$
@Whatcha say?! $red$GUMMY FROGS$black$!?$n$
All right! $Arancia$, you stay here! I'm going first!

\86\0c$n$
@Hey! That's no fair!$n$
I found them first!

\86\07$n$
@North of here is the water's edge.$n$
It's dark already so don't go and play in the sea!

\86\08$n$
@The sea's great isn't it?$n$
Just the sound of the waves clears my mind.

\86\07$n$
@Is...$n$
Is everyone all right...?

\86\02$n$
@That's my prey! Don't snatch it!$n$
$red$Go catch the one further in!$black$

\86\03$n$
@Help!!!$n$
Everyone's going to be killed!!!

\86\0c$n$
@What's going on?!$n$
What happened!?

\86\08$n$
@How should I know?!$n$
Why don't you go ask it yourself!?

\86\03$n$
@Those near the beach are in a tight spot...$n$
It's like we're completely surrounded by them.

\86\0c$n$
@What...?$n$
What's going on...?

\86\0f$n$
@The birds are acting strangely...$n$
I hope it's just my imagination...

\86\05$n$
@Ummm...$pause$ sorry for asking you to come here...$n$
But your birthday just passed didn't it?

\86\06$n$
@My birthday? It was quite a while back.$n$
What of it?

\86\06$n$
@Oh, I see...$n$
Thanks.

\86\05$n$
@And then, ummm, how do I say this...$n$
I, ummm...

\86\05$n$
@Oh...$n$
Okay...$pause$ see you later then...

\86\05$n$
@N-no! You don't have to be polite!$n$
If you don't like it, you can just throw it away!

\86\05$n$
@Ahhh...$n$
What's wrong with me...?

\86\05$n$
@I want to play with a crab...$n$
*sniff*

$Miss Madeleine$$n$
@I'm impressed, |\85\00!$n$
You've been studying haven't you?

\86\0c$n$
@You've managed to slip away from the Enigma's grasp...$n$
Heeheehee...

\86\0e$n$
@Yeeesss!$n$
I'm going to beat you up!

\86\0e$n$
@Look here! It's a hole!$n$
There's an $red$entrance to a cave$black$! $red$\86\0c is in there$black$! We have to go inside!

\86\0e$n$
@Yeeesss!$n$
Just leave \86\0c alone!

\86\0c (?)$n$
@Heh...$n$
Someone's come to interrupt us...

\86\02$n$
@That's not $Arancia$. It's a fake.$n$
It's an Enigma in disguise.

\86\0e$n$
@Huh?$n$
Huuuhhh?

\86\0c (?)$n$
@You leave me with no choice.$n$
I'll just take you by force!

$シフォン$$n$
@Near the cave's exit is a pot with doodles on its back.$n$
$red$A ricebird lies inside it.$black$

Puppet$n$
@A man needs to be full of resolve!$n$
He must be prepared to die when his turn comes!

Puppet$n$
@We're powerless aren't we...$n$
Isn't there anything we can do...?

Puppet$n$
@A man must be full of spirit!$n$
He mustn't be worried over anything!

Puppet$n$
@Ahhh, no no no!$n$
Why is it so dangerous?!

Traveling Putty$n$
@Why, hello there.$n$
Did you receive permission to enter the ruins? I want to too so I can continue my trip.$n$

$ミルフィ$$n$
@Don't die!$n$
I don't want anyone else to die!

Puppet$n$
@What happened?!$n$
Another killing!?

$ティラミス$$n$
@You guys are so loud.$n$
What happened?!

$ティラミス$$n$
@Even if you curse and scream, the dead won't come back to life.$n$
There's nothing we can do for those who died.

$ミルフィ$$n$
@Those are $red$blankets$black$.$n$
Grandfather, don't worry. Tomorrow, I'll hand them the $red$|\87\03$black$ and guide them through the ruins.

$ミルフィ$$n$
@Not you grandfather. I'm taking the travelers there.$n$
Grandfather, just take it easy and rest. Your body's shaking.

$ミルフィ$$n$
@No more...$n$
Please, no more deaths...

$ミルフィ$$n$
@This the house of $シフォン$, $トルーナ村$'s village chief.$n$
I am $シフォン$'s granddaughter, $ミルフィ$. Nice to meet you.

\86\0c$n$
@Hey wait! |\86\06!$n$
Just leave it for later! Sheesh!

\86\0e$n$
@We're not in a rush, so you can take us later!$n$
...

$ティラミス$$n$
@I'm the owner of the inn, $ティラミス$. Sorry, but we're closed right now.$n$
$red$Please come again later$black$.

$ティラミス$$n$
@Please take my heart...$pause$ and give it to...$n$
my...$pause$ brother...

$ミルフィ$$n$
@Why...?$n$
Just why...?

$ミルフィ$$n$
@This is the inn. Do you wish to stay the night?$n$
$red$It's free$black$ so stay as much as you want.

$ティラミス$$n$
@Another puppet died huh...$n$
What do you think...?

$ティラミス$$n$
@I see...$n$
So you're saying that you feel sorrow?

$ミルフィ$$n$
@Of course I do!!!$n$
One of our friends died you know!!!

$ティラミス$$n$
@I want your heart...$n$
I want to revive my brother...

$ミルフィ$$n$
@What are you saying...?$n$
Your brother is dead...

\86\0c$n$
@Whaaat?!$n$
She just went on ahead.

$スノウヘア$$n$
@Caw!$n$
Caw caw caw!!!

$ミルフィ$$n$
@I can't.$n$
I can't just leave $ティラミス$ alone.

\86\02$n$
@But there's no way we can let you go back yourself.$n$
$ティラミス$ might be waiting to ambush you!

\86\06$n$
@Just believe in destiny. Everything's carefully calculated for us.$n$
There's nothing in life that cannot be overcome.

\86\0c$n$
@What...why can't you do it?$n$
Why?

\86\02$n$
@Seriously!$n$
Just leave her!

\86\0c$n$
@Whaaattt?!$n$
We should chase after her.

\86\02$n$
@Can't the Enigmas distinguish between humans and buses...?$n$
They might have great magic powers but they're brain's the size of a peanut.

Balsamico$n$
@Anyhow, hop on. No need to be polite.$n$
Just hop on, relax, and make yourself at home!

Balsamico$n$
@Oh yeah, I did. I saw $red$|\86\0d$black$ and $red$|\86\07$black$. And also $red$|\86\08$black$ and
$red$|\86\03$black$. Those two sure are best buds aren't they?

Balsamico$n$
@Hahahahaha! $Kirsche$, you're still young!$n$
One day, you're going to be a twisted adult just like me! You know that don't you?!

\86\0c$n$
@Eeek!$n$
Ah, that surprised me!

Brave Envoy of Love$n$
@We are the $red$guards of the village chief of $ワクティ村$$black$! We are $red$Tarte$black$ and $red$Tatin$black$!$n$
And in between us is the village chief's $red$Sonny$black$. $red$Sonny$black$, you say something too!

Sonny$n$
@I'm not Sonny! I'm the village chief!$n$
I'll tell my father about anyone who opposes me and they'll lose their heads!

Sonny$n$
@You foreigners! You'd do well to leave quickly. This area is under the jurisdiction of we Envoys of Love!$n$
Recently, I have heard that there are Enigma prowling about.

\86\0c$n$
@But Sonny...$n$
We...

Sonny$n$
@I'm not Sonny! My name is Tortilla!$n$
I'm the chief of $ワクティ村$!

$ワクティ村$ villager$n$
@This is $red$$ワクティ村$$black$. It is the village of Envoys of Love.$n$
If you head south, you'll find $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$, a relic of an ancient civilization that flourished. They say that $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$ has been uninhabited for roughly 200 years.

$ワクティ村$ villager$n$
@This is the $red$village chief's house$black$.$n$
Make sure you pay your respects. He is a magnificent figure.

$ワクティ村$ villager$n$
@Recently, Enigma have been prowling around, even in the Light Realm.$n$
Some say they've seen Enigma around here too. Sonny is getting worried.

$ワクティ村$ villager$n$
@Sir Tortilla is a really kind person.$n$
Even though he's been ranting about how he'll kill the Enigmas, I don't think he actually will.

Gateau$n$
@I gave a $red$|\87\05$black$ to the 3 people who were just here so they could enter the $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$.$n$
If there's something you need to do at $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$, it would be wise to go together. I'll hand you a $red$|\87\05$black$ too.

Gateau$n$
@I see...$n$
To be honest, the 3 girls from before said they wanted to enter $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$ to save their friend. I handed them a $red$|\87\05$black$ but now I'm getting worried. If you're going to $red$$レーミッツ宮殿$$black$, could you make sure they're all right?

Gateau$n$
@Oh, Tortilla. I'm sorry.$n$
This is all in the name of love. It's empathy. In other words, love.

Sonny$n$
@How is that love?!$n$
Please take things seriously! You're not worthy of being the village chief anymore!

Gateau$n$
@That may be true. This village needs no village chief anymore.$n$
Everyone is able to regulate themselves.

Sonny$n$
@Travelers, you may use the $red$|\87\05$black$ as you wish.$n$
However, the Enigma is OUR enemy. We shall be the ones that kill it!

Sonny$n$
@Exactly!$n$
Let's go! Guards!

$ワクティ村$ villager$n$
@All my siblings are $red$Hunters of Love$black$.$n$
They work all day and night to save spirits that have been turned into ugly dodos.

$ナンプラ$$n$
@Hear hear. We're not opening them.$n$
Kill the strange monster then we'll talk.

$ナンプラ$$n$
@Hear hear. We want money too.$n$
After you kill the monster, give us 1000 Bura.

\86\0e$n$
@It smells like $red$|\86\07$black$!$n$
And $red$|\86\03$black$ too!

Sonny$n$
@Are you ignoring my warning...?$n$
Why must you deliberately enter this dangerous place...?

Tarte$n$
@Sonny...$n$
How about we lend them a hand and defeat the Enigma together...?

\86\02$n$
@Don't be stubborn. There's so many of us here.$n$
This is our chance to defeat the Enigma!

Tortilla$n$
@Why must we defeat them...?$pause$ What have they done to us?!$n$
Are they not just staying inside the palace because they're scared of the light...!?

Tarte$n$
@Sonny, we are but lowly Envoys of Love. I understand how you feel
Sonny, but...

Sonny$n$
@Fighting will only breed more fighting.$n$
What's important is love. If you understand that, then please accept my unconditional love.

\86\03$n$
@Yes, they're completely different from the ones at the beach.$n$ 
There's no way we can take on 3 of them...

\86\02$n$
@This is our chance, while $Lemon$'s got 1 covered...$n$
If we can deal with the remaining two one at a time...

Enigma$n$
@Heeheehee...$n$
What do you want me to do while I wait for you to fight him?

Enigma$n$
@Hahaha...$pause$ 2 "things"...$n$
It's an honor to be treated like insects...

\86\0e$n$
@Eeek! I want to perform fusion! I want to fuse with an Enigma and become stronger!$n$
I don't want to die!!!

Enigma$n$
@Hahaha.$n$
I'm glad you're so understanding.

Sonny$n$
@Bah! Me, a hero?!$n$
Are you saying I should return to the village and tell everyone$n$$n$
@Look at me! You should all fight like me!"!?

Tatin$n$
@Sir Tortilla!$n$
Let's return to the village! With you as the chief of $red$$ワクティ村$$black$!

Sonny$n$
@Thanks, my guards. And everyone else too.$n$
I hope we meet again somewhere.

\86\07$n$
@There's no helping it.$n$
Even if we curse the Enigma as our enemies and fight them, it doesn't change the fact that they must die.

\86\02$n$
@Let's go.$n$
$red$Let's find |\86\08 and |\86\0d.$black$

\86\03$n$
@That's right. And we also need to search for answers.$n$
I'm not going to feel any different towards the Enigmas unless I know why they are targeting us.

\86\08$n$
@Tch...!$n$
I let my guard down...

\86\03$n$
@Don't worry. My body's fine...$n$
Ugh...!

\86\08$n$
@You're not fine.$n$
|\86\07, |\86\06, can you take her back to the magic bus?

\86\03$n$
@I don't know what you're trying...$n$
But I don't want to always be the only one staying put and watching others!

\86\03$n$
@Don't call me that! It's true that...$n$
I was born with a frail body, but just treat me normally!

\86\08$n$
@I can't...$n$
Especially in your current state. If we slip up, you'll die.

\86\03$n$
@I...I don't know what you think, but I thought of us as best friends.$n$
Are you saying I can't even think that?

\86\02$n$
@No one's going to stop you.$n$
Besides, even if we said no, you'd still go anyways right?

Souris$n$
@Inside here, there's a lot of $red$gummy frogs$black$.$n$
If you want to catch the $red$gummy frogs$black$ inside, you need to pay me $red$5 |\87\19$black$.

Parmesan
@I am the head of this tower, Parmesan, maybe.$n$
Ah, I'm so idle, so idle, so busy, maybe.

\86\0d$n$
@This is kind of awkward to say since you saved me...$n$
But I was thinking things over, and I'm ready to be retooled into parts for the magic bus.

Balsamico$n$
@Hey, twerps!$pause$ You're just in time!$n$
Just now, I tried taking $Latte$ apart but his parts are so rusty I can't use any of them!

Almond$n$
@No, I'm not interested in humans!$n$
Go home! Go home!

Almond$n$
@Oh! An ancient machine! Nice! Good!$n$
Come on in!

Vin Blanc$n$
@Oh, you sorry machine!$n$
If our boss retools you, you'll be a real beauty!

Vin Rouge$n$
@Man, you guys brought us a darn good machine!$n$
Yeeehaaaaw! I just want to retool it!

Aurore$n$
@We just received our periodic report from below...$n$
Did anything happen?

Cardinal$n$
@This is the dwarf's tower, $red$$キード・モンガ$$black$.$n$
It sounds cliche, but a long time ago, there was a war of light and darkness. During that time, the Angel of Light's weapon was forged here, in $キード・モンガ$.

Salmis$n$
@Heh. Why's this fun you ask?$n$
Machines can't eat and breathe yet. But someday, someday they will.

Zingara$n$
@Only those with the $red$|\87\08$black$ can open this door.$n$
You can easily open it from the inside though.

\86\0e$n$
@In that case, let's return to the magic bus.$n$
It'd be bad to get involved any further.

\86\08$n$
@We've decided to look for $Latte$.$n$
$red$There's no need to swap out any party members.$black$

\86\0e$n$
@What happened to $Lemon$ and $Blueberry$?!$n$
Are $Peche$ and $Latte$ here too!?

Grenadine$n$
@How do the parts feel?! Do they work?$n$
Or is it no good?

Balsamico$n$
@OK! It's done! It worked!$n$
And $Latte$ still looks the same, so I'd say this is a huge success!

\86\0c$n$
@Let's worry about $Ganache$ before $Candy$! $Kirsche$ you idiot!$n$
Didn't you see Ganache?!

\86\09$n$
@Ah!$pause$ Where did you come from?$n$
Who are you?

Biscotti$n$
@The reason for this is that something may occur and $Miss Madeleine$ will say something along the lines of "Let's return home".$n$
Those who come back without a second thought will be expelled.

Principal Biscotti$n$
@Eek!$pause$ Well then, I shall take my leave!$n$
Have fun!

Piranha$n$
@Watch where you going!$n$
You blind or something?!

Piranha$n$
@You better pay your debt, you squid!$n$
Pay me $red$10 Bura$black$!

Piranha$n$
@You're really scummy.$n$
Fine, $red$10 Bura$black$.

Piranha$n$
@All right, I'll forgive you.$n$
Make sure you be careful from now on.

Melone$n$
@Do you want to try depositing some money with me?$n$
With my investing, it'll certainly double, and then double again, and double again, and just keep on doubling.

Melone$n$
@You can withdraw the money now if you want but...$n$
If you keep it deposited with me, it'll increase even further.

Melone$n$
@That's fine too! Here's the promised money.$n$
Perhaps fate will have us meet again somewhere!

\8a\ab
Ricebird$n$
@Chirp!!

Gusty$n$
@Hey, thanks for saving me. A long time ago, I was turned into a ricebird using magic and couldn't return to normal.$n$
Hey, you really saved me.

\86\06$n$
@I have a bad feeling. Something's coming.$n$
I'm going to explain the basics of battle so make sure you take it to heart.

\86\08$n$
@Why the long face? Did something happen?$n$
You should talk about it.

Inky$n$
@You want my help...? I hate those who are weak.$n$
Fight me...

\86\0a$n$
@If you have high $red$spirit$black$, the damage from magic attacks will be reduced.$n$
$Blueberry$ has a lot of spirit. Her body might be weak, but her heart is strong.

\86\07$n$
@Everyone! There's a problem!$n$
$Blueberry$'s didn't feel so well, and then she wasn't able to move, and then...$pause$ and then...

\86\0e$n$
@And then?!$n$
Calm down and tell us what happened!

\86\07$n$
@Ah, ah, ah, ahhh!$n$
I don't know where the beginning is.

\86\07$n$
@Ummm, the 3 of us were attacked by Enigmas at the gate.$n$
$Lemon$ used herself as a decoy and let us escape.

\86\03$n$
@Thanks for always looking out for me.$n$
But I don't want to be the only sitting out! I don't want that!

Magical creature$n$
@What?! You guys!?$n$
I'll make you spin around too, like the dwarfs.

Magical creature$n$
@Heeeee! Hahaha! This is the best!$n$
Spin round and round! Don't die on me you all!

Magical creature$n$
@What'd you say?!$n$
I won't forgive you!!! I'll kill you!!!

$ヌクマム$$n$
@He's $ブッチーネ３世$, a monster.$n$
Once he starts making dwarfs spins, they can't stop until they die.

$ヌクマム$$n$
@Hear hear.$n$
You're our savior. Feel free to pass through this gate.

Balsamico$n$
@It's no good! The magic bus is buried in sand!$n$
It looks like $red$we can't use the magic bus here$black$.

$Miss Madeleine$$n$
@Our long camp begins now. During camp, you will be away from your families and so you must take care of everything on your own. The first 1 or 2 days will be fun I expect, but as camp continues, there will be people who feel lonely or who get into fights with others. There will be happy times and tough times. But it will be a valuable experience for you all. The more experience you have, the stronger you will become.$n$
Does being strong mean you will never lose to anyone? No, that is incorrect. If you are truly strong, you will have no need to fight in the first place.

Balsamico$n$
@Sorry! It's totally broken.$n$
That function can't be used yet.

Hunter of Love$n$
@I can restore spirits that have been turned into dodos but...$n$
I can't do anything about humans or other animals that have been turned into dodos.

Hunter of Love$n$
@Why were they turned into dodos?!$n$
Why!? What is going on!?

Hunter of Love$n$
@I hear spirits crying out...$n$
They are pleading for my help...

Hunter of Love$n$
@Everyone says dodos are ugly but... I don't think so.$n$
They just smell a little bad, that's all.

Wandering Pot$n$
@The interactions between magical elements is complicated isn't it?$n$
We each try to learn a bit of it. Those pots who aren't enthusiastic about learning magic are fake pots.

Wandering Pot$n$
@Pots don't have belly buttons. I guess that's obvious.$n$
Hahaha.

Hunter of Love$n$
@Many people are embarrassed when they discuss love...$n$
Since I'm an Envoy of Love, I'm embarrassed just by existing.

Worcestershire$n$
@So you see...$n$
Eh, where should I start explaining from?

Worcestershire$n$
@Magic dolls require some power in order to operate. Once you combine the 5 parts, you can $red$bewitch$black$ a magic doll with an ally's soul.$n$
But if your ally's $red$experience points$black$ is lower than the $red$power usage$black$, then the magic doll won't operate well. So in the beginning, there's not much point in creating a flashy magic doll. You have to start small and be patient.

Balsamico$n$
@Sorry! I'm feeling a bit sick right now.$n$
Let's warp later!

Worcestershire$n$
@There ain't room for my magic doll with this large group you have.$n$
Come back with fewer people.

Worcestershire$n$
@Look, $red$there should be MD parts just lying around here$black$ so go search around.$n$
I'm counting on you.

$Miss Madeleine$$n$
@Ahahaha. As expected of you, |\85\00.$n$
In that case, do you know about the $red$help screen$black$?

Worcestershire$n$
@When you think of $red$magic dolls$black$, you think of $red$combos$black$.$n$
If you use magic that's the same element as the soul you bewitched with, you can have the $red$magic doll$black$ use call magic and then attack with the character whose soul you used. Since $red$magic dolls$black$ can't recover MP, that'll also let you conserve MP.

$Miss Madeleine$$n$
@The one on top is called the $red$start button$black$. If you press it, you'll open up the $red$menu$black$ and be able to do things like make preparations during your journey. Things you can do after you open your $red$menu$black$ include using items, managing equipment, looking at your maps, and more...$n$
Well, for more information, you can check the $red$help screen$black$ when you open your $red$menu$black$. |\85\00, do you know about the $red$help screen$black$?

Puppet shopkeeper$n$
@Thank you very much. Come again.$n$
Don't forget to equip your shirts and shoes on the $red$equipment$black$ page in the $red$menu$black$.

Gateau$n$
@I heard Sonny went on a journey. I knew that he would.$n$
However, I believe that one day he will return a greater Envoy of Love than before.

\86\10$n$
@Ah! Look there! Something's there!$n$
What is that?!

\86\02$n$
@Wait up, anyone could have entered here.$n$
If we open it up, we might just find that it's empty.

\86\05$n$
@No, I'm scared...$n$
Something's here. I'm sure of it.

Oyster$n$
